  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "Tr\u1EADn chi\u1EBFn lan tr\xE0n kh\u1EAFp x\u1EE9. H\xF4m \u1EA5y, s\u1ED1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u1EBFt v\xEC g\u1EB7p nguy hi\u1EC3m trong r\u1EEBng \u0111\xF4ng h\u01A1n ch\u1EBFt v\xEC \u0111\xE1nh nhau.\xC1p-xa-l\xF4m ch\u1EBFt "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v9"
  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "\xC1p-xa-l\xF4m t\xECnh c\u1EDD g\u1EB7p qu\xE2n \u0110a-v\xEDt. Trong khi \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m \u0111ang c\u1EE1i l\u1EEBa ch\u1EA1y th\xEC n\xF3 chui b\xEAn d\u01B0\u1EDBi c\xE1c nh\xE0nh r\u1EADm r\u1EA1p c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t c\xE2y s\u1ED3i. \u0110\u1EA7u c\u1EE7a \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m v\u01B0\u1EDBng v\xE0o nh\xE0nh c\xE2y, c\xF2n con l\u1EEBa ch\u1EA1y tho\xE1t. Th\u1EBF l\xE0 \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m b\u1ECB treo l\u01A1 l\u1EEDng tr\xEAn kh\xF4ng . "), mdx("h6", {
