  }, "v16"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i Gi\xF4-\xE1p th\u1ED5i k\xE8n, qu\xE2n s\u0129 li\u1EC1n th\xF4i \u0111u\u1ED5i theo ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCDt-ra-en v\xEC Gi\xF4-\xE1p c\u1EA3n h\u1ECD. "), mdx("h6", {
