  }, "v17"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c binh s\u0129 c\u1EE7a Gi\xF4-\xE1p khi\xEAng x\xE1c \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m qu\u0103ng trong m\u1ED9t h\u1ED1 l\u1EDBn gi\u1EEFa r\u1EEBng r\u1ED3i l\u1EA5y \u0111\xE1 l\u1EA5p l\xEAn. C\xF2n t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCDt-ra-en \u0111\u1EC1u ch\u1EA1y tr\u1ED1n v\u1EC1 nh\xE0 m\xECnh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "L\xFAc \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng, anh d\u1EF1ng m\u1ED9t tr\u1EE5 k\u1EF7 ni\u1EC7m cho m\xECnh trong thung l\u0169ng Vua. Anh b\u1EA3o, \"Ta kh\xF4ng c\xF3 con trai n\u1ED1i d\xF5i.\" Cho n\xEAn anh l\u1EA5y t\xEAn m\xECnh \u0111\u1EB7t cho tr\u1EE5 \u0111\xF3 v\xE0 ng\xE0y nay v\u1EABn g\u1ECDi l\xE0 \u0110\xE0i K\u1EF7 ni\u1EC7m \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m.Gi\xF4-\xE1p b\xE1o tin cho \u0110a-v\xEDt "), mdx("h6", {
