  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Vua h\u1ECFi, \"Ch\xE0ng trai tr\u1EBB \xC1p-xa-l\xF4m b\xECnh y\xEAn kh\xF4ng?\" A-hi-m\xE1t th\u01B0a, \"Khi Gi\xF4-\xE1p sai t\xF4i \u0111i, t\xF4i nghe c\xF3 ti\u1EBFng huy\xEAn n\xE1o nh\u01B0ng t\xF4i kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt chuy\u1EC7n g\xEC.\" "), mdx("h6", {
